{"article_id":"HKJPwNOMMfixUlp2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"J.K. Rowling at a gala performance of the play Harry Potter and the Cursed Child parts One and Two , in London , England , in 2016 .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"( Neil Hall/Reuters )","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Unchallenged , a British judge ' s decision could mean","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that countless others lose their jobs","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"for stating the obvious .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Twitter has exploded in outrage","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"because J. K. Rowling , author of the Harry Potter books , is an alleged \" TERF. \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"That ' s right ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"a \" trans-exclusionary radical feminist. \"","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"This ridiculous slur was invented by people","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"who insist on denying the science of sex","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"and who want to take out their rage on nonbelievers , and on dissenting women in particular .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Prominent male transgender activists such as Charlotte Clymer have gone full hysterical .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"\" For several years , there has been substantial concern","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"that J.K. Rowling is transphobic , \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Clymer tweeted ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"referring ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"I presume ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"to the time","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Rowling followed the women ' s rights campaigner Magdalen Berns on Twitter .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" I admit","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that I held out","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that one of my childhood heroes was simply being misunderstood .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"This morning , that was dashed","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"when she defended a researcher","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"who was fired for transphobic tweets . \"","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"\" As a gay man","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"that found safety in Hogwarts throughout my childhood , \"","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"tweeted Shamir Sanni .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"\" Knowing","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that Trans people wouldn ' t be able to have that safety breaks my heart. \"","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Does Mr. Sanni realize","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that Hogwarts isn ' t real ?","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"To those of us","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"who have been following the steady erosion of women ' s rights , child safeguarding , and medical science ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Rowling ' s intervention was very welcome .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Here is what she said :","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"But force women out of their jobs","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"for stating","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that sex is real ?","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"# IStandWithMaya","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"# ThisIsNotADrill","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"- J.K. Rowling","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"( @ jk_rowling )","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"December 19 , 2019","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"As for what she is referring to , it is merely the latest in the transgender war on employment rights .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"In October , I wrote about a doctor","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who was sacked for his disbelief in transgenderism .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"David Mackereth M.D . had worked for nearly 30 years for the British National Health Service","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"without attracting a single complaint .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"when he signaled at a training session ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"after being confronted with a hypothetical scenario ,","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"that he felt unable to disregard his belief in the immutability of sex ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"he was dismissed .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Later , a British employment judge ruled","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"that his employer ' s decision was fair","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"because Mackereth ' s belief","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"that a person can not become the opposite sex","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"was \" incompatible with human dignity. \"","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"This week , another employment judge made an almost identical ruling in relation to Maya Forstater , a tax expert","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"who lost her job","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"for expressing this same belief in various tweets .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"As with Mackereth , Forstater was hoping to defend her right","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to express her beliefs","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"by using the U.K. ' s anti-discrimination law , the Equality Act of 2010 .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"This law was intended to prevent discrimination on the basis of a range of characteristics","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"including \" belief. \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"As I explained at the time :","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"The legal precedent for a case like this ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"as referred to throughout the judgment ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"comes from Grainger v. Nicholson ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"argued in 2010 .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"In Grainger , Nicholson ' s lawyers successfully argued","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that his belief in climate change was a philosophical position","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"worthy of protection under the \" religion or belief \" clause of the Equality Act .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"Nicholson ' s environmentalism was then used","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"to establish the following criteria for the category of \" belief \" :","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"That it be \" genuinely held . \"","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"That it be a belief","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"and not an opinion or viewpoint","depth":16},{"id":81,"text":"( e.g. , this or that political affiliation or preference ) .","depth":16},{"id":82,"text":"That it be concerning \" a weighty and substantial aspect of human life and behavior . \"","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"That it have \" a certain level of cogency , seriousness , cohesion and importance . \"","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"That it be \" worthy of respect in a democratic society","depth":17},{"id":85,"text":"[ and ] be not incompatible with human dignity","depth":18},{"id":86,"text":"and not conflict with the fundamental rights of others \"","depth":18},{"id":87,"text":"( emphasis added ) .","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"Forstater ' s belief , on trial , was simply","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"that \" ' sex ' is a material reality","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"which should not be conflated with ' gender ' or ' gender identity. ' \"","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Further , that \" being female is an immutable biological fact ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"not a feeling or an identity .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Moreover , sex matters .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"It is important to be able to talk about and take action against the discrimination , violence and oppression","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that still affect women and girls","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"because they were born female . \"","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The legal question is whether this belief","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"- or her lack of belief in transgenderism :","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"\" that everyone has an inner ' gender '","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"which may be the same as or different to their sex at birth ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and that gender effectively trumps sex ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"so that ' trans men are men '","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"and ' trans women are women ' \" -","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"amounts to a philosophical belief","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"as defined and protected by the Equality Act of 2010 .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Forstater explains","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"that the reason for her involvement in the gender debate was that \" she first became concerned about proposed changes to the Gender Recognition Act 2004 in 2017","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"because of proposals for a move","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"to permitting people to self-identify their gender. \"","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"After a year of researching","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"and formulating her view ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"she began tweeting about it in August 2018 .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Some of those tweets included :","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" UK gov consultation","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"on reforming the GenderRecognitionAct -","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"proposes to dramatically change scope of the law ;","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"from requiring medical diagnosis of gender dysphoria for change of sex on birth certificate ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"to using the basis of ' self identification ' ... \"","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"\" I share the concerns of @ fairplaywomen","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that radically expanding the legal definition of ' women '","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"so that it can include both males and females","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"makes it a meaningless concept ,","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"and will undermine women ' s rights & protections for vulnerable women & girls . ... \"","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" Some transgender people have cosmetic surgery .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"But most retain their birth genitals .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Everyone ' s equality and safety should be protected ,","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"but women and girls lose out on privacy , safety and fairness","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"if males are allowed into changing rooms , dormitories , prisons , sports teams . \"","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"The judge also notes","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"that Forstater had shown support for \" campaigns","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"where the definition ' woman , wʊmən , noun , adult human female ' is put on billboards ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"projected onto buildings","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"and printed on T shirts. \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Just imagine !","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"The judge highlighted","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that Forstater had explained to her employers in October 2018 :","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"I have been told that it is offensive to say","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"\" transwomen are men \"","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"or that women means \" adult human female \" .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"However","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"since these statement are true","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"I will continue to say them .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"Yes the definition of females excludes males","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"( but includes women","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"who do not conform with gendered norms ) .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Policy debates","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"where facts are viewed as offensive","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"are dangerous .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"I would of course respect anyone ' s self-definition of their gender identity in any social and professional context ;","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"I have no desire or intention to be rude to people .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"The judge characterized Forstater ' s comments as proving","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"that \" she considers","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"there are two sexes , male and female ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"there is no spectrum in sex","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"and there are no circumstances whatsoever","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"in which a person can change from one sex to another , or to being of neither sex. \"","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"Is this not a reasonable belief ?","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"One","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"that ' s commonly held","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"and worthy of protection ?","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"The judge also noted","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"that \" she would generally seek to be polite to trans persons","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"and would usually seek to respect their choice of pronoun","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"but would not feel bound to. \"","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"Again , is this not a reasonable position ?","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"The judge himself notes","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"that Forstater ' s approach \" is largely that currently adopted by the law ,","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"which still treats sex as binary","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"as defined on a birth certificate. \"","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"And yet he decides","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"that the answer","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"to whether one should be protected from being fired ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"simply for politely expressing a belief in biological sex ,","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"is no .","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"This is judicial activism , and deeply unfair .","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"J. K. Rowling is exactly right .","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"For all our sakes , it must be overturned .","depth":6},{"id":178,"text":"Institute","depth":4},{"id":179,"text":"( NRI )","depth":4},{"id":180,"text":"is the nonprofit 501 ( c ) ( 3 )","depth":5},{"id":181,"text":"journalistic think tank","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"that supports the NR mission and 14 NRI fellows","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"( including this author ! ) ,","depth":6},{"id":184,"text":"allowing them to do what they do best :","depth":6},{"id":185,"text":"Advance principled and practical conservative journalism .","depth":6},{"id":186,"text":"NRI is currently in the midst of its End-of-Year Fund Appeal","depth":4},{"id":187,"text":"and seeks to raise over $ 200,000","depth":5},{"id":188,"text":"to support the work of the NRI fellows .","depth":5},{"id":189,"text":"Please consider giving a generous end-of-year tax-deductible contribution to NRI .","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"Your gift , along with all those from the NR Nation , will provide the essential fuel for our mission","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"to defend those consequential principles","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"for which has fought since 1955 ,","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"and for which , with your support , it will carry the fight far into the future .","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"Thank you for your consideration .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":389,"left":372,"right":388,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":372,"left":239,"right":371,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":196,"right":238,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":198,"right":237,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":2,"right":197,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":225,"right":236,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":204,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":5,"right":203,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":6,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":199,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":201,"left":200,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":12,"right":223,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":210,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":206,"right":209,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":205,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"N